column5: Such respect. What a fucking badass. RIP Alexander
All I want is a hug, so totally. Like, I legitimately would cry if someone hugged me. Here's my hug to you, brother/sister. *hug*
It happened to me over one person. I've lost her as a friend since, partially because of my infatuation, and it's ruined me.

I feel the same, even with my very different situation. I think everyone and everything is becoming less joyful overall, though I wish it wasn't. Have a Merry Christmas, at least as Merry as you can make it.
Update: We’re good again. We’ve gotten past that awkwardness... I know I still feel the same way about her, but it can never happen. But I’m thankful that I still have her, as a friend.
She really does mean so much to me... She’s one of the only things I appreciate about my life right now. Thanks islamic-terrorist69
